margin:0}.c10{color:inherit;text-decoration:inherit}.c2{color:#1155cc;text-decoration:underline}.c3{margin-left:36pt;padding-left:0pt}.c11{font-size:14pt}.c1{font-size:12pt}.c5{font-weight:bold}.c6{height:11pt}.c7{margin-left:36pt}.c4{font-size:10pt}.title{padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;font-size:26pt;padding-bottom:3pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}.subtitle{padding-top:0pt;color:#666666;font-size:15pt;padding-bottom:16pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}li{color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:"Arial"}p{margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:"Arial"}h1{padding-top:20pt;color:#000000;font-size:20pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}h2{padding-top:18pt;color:#000000;font-size:16pt;padding-bottom:6pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}h3{padding-top:16pt;color:#434343;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:4pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}h4{padding-top:14pt;color:#666666;font-size:12pt;padding-bottom:4pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}h5{padding-top:12pt;color:#666666;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:4pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}h6{padding-top:12pt;color:#666666;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:4pt;font-family:"Arial";line-height:1.15;page-break-after:avoid;font-style:italic;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left}</style><p class="c0"><span class="c5 c11">Changes in Solr Schema</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c11 c5"></span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_ckhiuz7fod8f-0 start" start="1"><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1 c5">Tag Document</span></li></ol><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c1">Tag Documents are on 10.10.16.71 solr instance. </span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c1 c2"><a class="c10" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://10.10.16.72:8985/solr/collection1/select?q%3D*%253A*%26wt%3Dxml%26indent%3Dtrue&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEGwyWbinZul7EpkF-I7o6KSmPhMQ">http://10.10.16.72:8985/solr/collection1/select?q=*%3A*&amp;wt=xml&amp;indent=true</a></span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">        Following fields have been added to schema for tag document : </span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_id</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;string&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text_general_tight&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name_text</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name_string</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text_general_tight_nonstopwords&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name_without_special_chars</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;course_facet&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_entity</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;string&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_description</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c4 c5">tag_quality_factor</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;float&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_synonyms</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text_general_tight&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name_edgeNGram</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text_edgeNGram&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_name_keywordEdgeNGram</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;keyword_edgeNGram&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_synonyms_edgeNGram</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;text_edgeNGram&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">tag_synonyms_keywordEdgeNGram</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;keyword_edgeNGram&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Variations of tag name like tag_name, tag_name_text, tag_name_string, tag_name_without_special_chars are for better matching of tags in the search results which the N-gram versions are helpful in showing suggestions to the user when the user types in something in the search box(auto-suggestor).</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Synonyms are not stored as a separate tag document rather they are stored in the tag document of which they are synonym of. </span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1 c5">Tag Quality Factor</span><span class="c1">  :It is score based on number of followers of tag, questions and discussions associated with the tag. </span></p><p class="c0 c6 c7"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0 c7"><span class="c1">Quality Factor</span><span class="c1 c5"> </span><span class="c1">= (followMultiplicativeFactor * followCount) + (questionMultiplicativeFactor * questionsLinkedCount) + (discussionMultiplicativeFactor * discussionLinkedCount) </span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">As the followers of tags keeps on changing and questions/discussion associated with them will also keep on changing, we will need to update the tag quality score regularly. </span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">A CRON(</span><span class="c1 c5">APICron::indexTagsWithRecentActivities</span><span class="c1">) will update the tag quality score on daily basis. This cron will pick all those tags for which any activity has been done on follow/unfollow, tagging/untagging and re-index them. Re-indexing of these tags will update the tag quality score in the solr-index as well as in the database.</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Other sections from where tags will be added to indexing queue :</span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_y8rzl6f1aff-0 start" start="1"><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1">Add tag.</span></li><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1">Edit tag.</span></li><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1">Delete tag.</span></li></ol><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1 c5">2. User Document</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">We will be using user document for user search and autosuggestions. </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">There is already a solr instance running on 10.10.16.72 server for LDB search.</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c2 c1"><a class="c10" href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://10.10.16.72:8985/solr/collection1/select?q%3D*%253A*%26wt%3Dxml%26indent%3Dtrue&amp;sa=D&amp;usg=AFQjCNEGwyWbinZul7EpkF-I7o6KSmPhMQ">http://10.10.16.72:8985/solr/collection1/select?q=*%3A*&amp;wt=xml&amp;indent=true</a></span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">We are using the same instance. Three fields has been added to this schema : </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">   </span></p><p class="c0"><span>   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5">user_ana_points</span><span>&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span>   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5">user_name_facet</span><span>&quot; type=&quot;text_facet&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span>   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5">user_name_edgeNGram</span><span>&quot; type=&quot;text_edgeNGram&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">User’s AnA points will be fetched from </span><span class="c1 c5">userpointsystembymodule </span><span class="c1">table. </span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">To update these AnAPoints a CRON has been created(</span><span class="c1 c5">APICron::indexUsersWithChangedAnAPoints</span><span class="c1">) which will pick-up all those user’s whose ana-points have changed and index them.</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1 c5">3. Question/Discussion Document</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Questions and discussion are currently being indexed on two solr instances</span></p><ol class="c8 lst-kix_7n80m59cn81r-0 start" start="1"><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1">10.10.16.71</span></li><li class="c0 c3"><span class="c1">10.10.16.82</span></li></ol><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">10.10.16.82 has some more fields as compared to the other instance. Question and discussion schema on 82 instance is a new one. We are using 82 instance for question/discussion search, related question/discussion. </span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">Following fields has been added to schema of Solr(82) instance : </span></p><p class="c0"><span>   </span><span class="c4">&lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_objective</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_objectiveparent</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_manual</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_manualparent</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_background</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c4">   &lt;field name=&quot;</span><span class="c5 c4">thread_tags_backgroundparent</span><span class="c4">&quot; type=&quot;int&quot; multiValued=&quot;true&quot; indexed=&quot;true&quot; stored=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</span></p><p class="c0 c6"><span class="c4"></span></p><p class="c0"><span class="c1">These fields will be used in finding out related question/discussions. </span></p></div><div id="footer"><span>